title: The Garrett Wonders Memorial Criterium, Westervill
Kings CX TT Series
description: Kings CX TT - a cyclocross time trial designed to build your skills and power leading up to the cyclocross season.
course: Each week\'s course will be different. Some weeks it will be long straights and power building. Some weeks might have single track included. Some weeks may have sand and barriers.
registration: Registration day of only on site. Registration fee is limited to insurance costs only. Must be a member of Queen City Wheels to participate.
notes:
3 categories - beginner, intermediate, advanced multiplied by 2 genders = 6 different races. Racers will be sent off one at a time like a real time trial at 20 second intervals.

Beginner will do 1 lap, no more than 3.6 miles of grass circuit.
Intermediate will do 2 laps, no more than 7.2 miles of grass circuit.
Advanced will do 3 laps, no more than 10.8 miles of grass circuit.
